{"tid":2056114,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"首爾一個教會設施新增8人確診 患者全部是中國人","createTime":"2020-06-08T12:37:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-08T12:51:29.000Z","uid":212626,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"bb8253d496dba25ab20430a846441c7cbd4cc079","tid":2056114,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T12:37:17.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】南韓首爾一個中國人教會設施，懷疑出現群聚感染，多人確診新型冠狀病毒。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">有關的教會設施位於首爾市九老區，累計已經有9人受感染。當地有報道稱，患者全部是中國人</span>，日前出現的首宗病例，是設施的住客在到訪過首爾一間，近日爆發群聚感染的保健品推銷公司後確診，設施其餘33名住客和3名教會相關人士，進行病毒檢測後，有8人呈陽性。<br />\n<br />\n當局已下令關閉有關教會和設施，並對超過150名信徒和設施居民進行調查。<br />\n<br />\n南韓過去一日新增38宗確診個案，當中33宗屬於本地社區感染，全部位於首都圈首爾、仁川和京畿道等地區，共五百多間學校決定，延遲要求學生到校上課，以免引發更大規模的連鎖感染。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=393743\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D393743&d=N73AYdKZ8ITSJgwUZ5%2B19ltf78QfJQp2bpA%2BRTfa5cI%3D&h=4b649d66\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D393743&h=2f166e6b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=393743</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a04a575249c344bb9421090156048cbe66867858","tid":2056114,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T12:44:12.000Z","msg":"特登放毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59f0352aa867c8c9ebc8c26881022601a16459f4","tid":2056114,"uid":293529,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T12:44:26.000Z","msg":"生化武器？？？"},{"pid":"2ed5c2100ace64fe035c281c7a1691bb990d2db8","tid":2056114,"uid":21545,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"59f0352aa867c8c9ebc8c26881022601a16459f4","tid":2056114,"uid":293529,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T12:44:26.000Z","msg":"生化武器？？？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTi